29 MayDeputy President Kgalema Motlanthe will brief the media on the Gauteng Freeway Improvement Project following an update report to Cabinet by the Inter-Ministerial Committee which he chairs. The Inter-Ministerial Committee comprises of Ministers of Finance, Transport, Monitoring and Evaluation as well as Administration, Environmental Affairs and Public Enterprises.Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Thursday 31 May 2012 Time: 09h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town There will be a video link up to the GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, cnr Sisulu and Madiba Sts, PretoriaRSVP by email to Pheliswa Sebati (Pretoria) or Sbongile Dalasile, sbongile@gcis.gov.za 0712921006 (Cape Town).Enquiries Jimmy Manyi Cell: 0823793454 Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)